{{!--
  Maintainer notes (not emitted in G-code):
  - Carvera 3-axis post — Smoothieware-based firmware.
  - Supports Carvera's 6-slot automatic tool changer (ATC): T1–T6.
  - T0 = wireless probe, T-1 = no tool. This template uses T1 by default.
  - After M6 tool change, the machine automatically probes tool length.
  - G43 H(tool#) applies tool length compensation; G49 cancels it.
  - CRITICAL: Uses M2 for program end, NOT M30 — M30 on Smoothieware may delete
    the file from the SD card.
  - Spindle range: 6000–15000 RPM. S value comes from dialect snippet.
  - G4 P2 dwell after spindle start lets the spindle reach commanded RPM.
  - M9 at end turns off coolant/vacuum.
  - Lines starting with ";" are operator-visible comments in output.
  - Template context keys: resources/posts/README.md (PostContext / renderPost).
--}}
; Makera Carvera — 3-Axis G-code
; Machine: {{machine.name}} — {{machine.id}}
{{#if operationLabel}}; Operation: {{operationLabel}}
{{/if}}; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; SAFETY CHECKLIST:
; [1] Workpiece securely clamped to table
; [2] Correct tool loaded in ATC slot (T1–T6)
; [3] Work coordinate system (WCS) zeroed — use G10 L20 P1 or controller UI
; [4] Air-cut first: spindle off, Z raised, 10% feed override
; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; UNVERIFIED G-CODE — verify every line against your Carvera firmware docs
; before running on the machine.
; Before production: dry run — spindle off, Z high, feed reduced.
; Compare a short program to a known-good file from Makera CAM.
; See docs/MACHINES.md — safe Z, WCS, units, spindle M-codes.
; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; ATC: Carvera 6-slot auto tool changer (T1–T6). T0 = probe, T-1 = no tool.
; After M6, the machine automatically probes tool length.
; G43 H(tool#) applies tool length compensation.
; G49 cancels tool length compensation at program end.
; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
; Work area (mm): {{machine.workAreaMm.x}} x {{machine.workAreaMm.y}} x {{machine.workAreaMm.z}}
; Spindle range: {{machine.minSpindleRpm}}–{{machine.maxSpindleRpm}} RPM
; ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
G21              ; millimeters
G90              ; absolute positioning
G17              ; XY plane
{{#if wcsLine}}; Active work offset — verify fixture zero matches G54–G59 selection
{{wcsLine}}
{{/if}}
; --- Tool change (ATC) ---
; Verify tool number matches the slot loaded in the Carvera ATC.
M6 T{{#if toolNumber}}{{toolNumber}}{{else}}1{{/if}}            ; select tool {{#if toolNumber}}{{toolNumber}}{{else}}1{{/if}} and execute tool change (auto-probes length)
G43 H{{#if toolNumber}}{{toolNumber}}{{else}}1{{/if}}           ; apply tool length compensation for tool {{#if toolNumber}}{{toolNumber}}{{else}}1{{/if}}

; Safe retract and spindle start
G0 Z{{machine.workAreaMm.z}} ; safe Z retract
{{spindleOn}}
G4 P2            ; dwell 2s for spindle to reach speed

; --- Toolpath ---
{{#each toolpathLines}}
{{this}}
{{/each}}
; --- end toolpath ---

; --- End ---
{{spindleOff}}
G49              ; cancel tool length compensation
G0 Z{{machine.workAreaMm.z}} ; retract Z
G0 X0 Y0        ; park X Y
M9               ; coolant/vacuum off
M2               ; program end (NOT M30 — M30 may delete file on Smoothieware)
